price.name: Super Sparpreis
price.description:
You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.description:

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.name: Flexpreis
price.description:
With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.name: Flexpreis
price.description:
With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

price.name: Super Sparpreis
price.description:
You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.name: Flexpreis
price.description:

Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.name: Flexpreis
price.description:
With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.name: Flexpreis
price.description:
With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

price.name: Super Sparpreis
price.description:
You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.name: Flexpreis
price.description:
With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.

price.name: Super Sparpreis
price.description:
You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

You can use all trains and IC Bus services indicated on your ticket. You can use any local train (i.e. RE, RB, S). Passengers on train and IC Bus services with mandatory reservation must reserve a seat. Your ticket does not entitle you to use the DB Lounge. Ihre Fahrkarte enthält kein City-Ticket.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) of your ticket is excluded.

price.name: Flexpreis
price.description:
With an ICE ticket you can use all trains on the day of travel, with an IC/EC ticket you can use any Intercity or Eurocity as well as local trains.
Cancellation (exchange or refund) before the 1st day of validity free, thereafter 19,00 EUR.
